date Balance''' check box selected. *:The box is available if the ''Parent-Child Customer Relationship'' feature is enabled on the [HelpRoot_FormReference\CS_10_00_00|Enable/Disable Features] form. *:For details, see [HelpRoot_Financials\AR__MNG_ParentChild|Managing Parent-Child Relationships].
