With the Acumatica ERP reports related to taxes, you can view key tax-related information. If a report contains data links, you can easily drill down from the report to any supporting details. ((({S:Hint}
A report includes only the objects or entities that the user running the report is authorized to access, based on the user&rsquo;s roles and membership in restriction groups. 
)))
 All tax-related reports can be generated in different formats, including PDF and HTML, and can be printed or sent by email. For more information about reports, see [HelpRoot_Interface\Report_Processing_Options|Reports].{br}

Each of the topics of this chapter provides reference information about a particular Acumatica ERP report, including details about the applicable report parameters you can use to select the exact data you want to view and analyze.

